{"tid":783987,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[on9 Google]Android 9 Pie 完全封殺通話錄音功能","createTime":"2018-08-18T04:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T19:39:51.000Z","uid":58335,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"018dd077c83d5cf37798d6a64f10064f569d6faf","tid":783987,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:15:36.000Z","msg":"好做唔做, Google on99,關你撚事咩o) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAndroid 9 Pie 雖然新增唔少新功能，甚至加入 AI 🇨🇳🇨🇳優化🇨🇳🇨🇳操作，但同時亦有功能正式在這一版起遭到 Google 封殺。<br />\n<br />\n所講的，其實就係對唔少用家來講都幾實用的「通話錄音」。最近有開發者發現，升級上 Android 9 Pie 後，已經無法在不 Root 機的狀態下，繼續使用通話錄音功能。<br />\n<br />\n其實今次已非 Google 首次封殺通話錄音，雖然早期版本 Android 一度內置相關 API，但已經被 Google 在 Android 6.0 開始刪去，雖然用家之後仍然可以用 ACR、Call Recorder 之類的第三方 App 錄下通話內容，但在 Android 9 Pie 開始，連第三方通話錄音也被 Google 封殺。<br />\n<br />\n平時有用開通話錄音的用家，在有解決方法出現之前，揀手機時可能要避開 Android 9 Pie 了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news/android-9-pie-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews%2Fandroid-9-pie-%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%258C%2584%25E9%259F%25B3%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD&d=Jjntxr48oCGt5aGYjZmvnxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f101592d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news/android-9-pie-%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA%E9%80%9A%E8%A9%B1%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B3%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD</a>"},{"pid":"505c8edf2969ffc46d5028f122ac23b10228a9dd","tid":783987,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T04:35:07.000Z","msg":"美國唔俾錄音"},{"pid":"cd5a7f79516ac0c28e5a7fe8bf57a220fc831a39","tid":783987,"uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"505c8edf2969ffc46d5028f122ac23b10228a9dd","tid":783987,"uid":113000,"like":6,"dislike":1,"sc